title: Duel Masters VS
synopsis: The most anticipated card game, Duel Masters had returned after 2 years since the battle in the past season. However, Katta Kirifuda once the strongest duelist, is now a year 2 middle school student and had lost his passion of dueling throughout the 2 years, and dreams of curry bread every day.
voices: ['Sugawara, Masayoshi', 'Tange, Sakura', 'Kobayashi, Yumiko', 'Ishino, Ryuuzou', 'Uchiyama, Kouki', 'Mizusawa, Fumie']
